"docs/post/zui-duan-lu.html", "labels": ["\u6a21\u677f"], "postTitle": "\u6700\u77ed\u8def", "postUrl": "post/zui-duan-lu.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/Vynor/Vynor.github.io/issues/10", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 3520, "description": "## Dijkstra ##\r\n\u5355\u6e90\u6c47\u6700\u77ed\u8def\uff0c\u8981\u6c42\u56fe\u4e0a**\u4e0d\u5b58\u5728**\u8d1f\u6743\u8fb9\r\n\u65f6\u95f4\u590d\u6742\u5ea6\u4e3a $O((N+M)logN)$\r\n```c++\r\nvector<pair<int, int>> edge[N];\r\n\r\nint n, m, s;\r\nint dist[N];\r\n\r\nset<pair<int, int>> q;\r\n\r\nvoid dij(int s){\r\n    memset(dist, 127, sizeof dist);\r\n    dist[s] = 0; q.clear();\r\n    for (int i = 1; i <= n; i ++ ) \r\n        q.insert(make_pair(dist[i], i));\r\n    while (!q.empty()){\r\n        int x = q.begin()->second;\r\n        q.erase(q.begin());\r\n        if (dist[x] > 1 << 30) break;//\u65e0\u6cd5\u62b5\u8fbex\r\n        for (auto [y, v]:edge[x])\r\n            if (dist[y] > dist[x] + v){\r\n                q.erase(make_pair(dist[y], y));\r\n                dist[y] = dist[x] + v;\r\n                q.insert(make_pair(dist[y], y));\r\n            }\r\n    }    \r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Bellman-Ford ##\r\nBellman\u2013Ford \u7b97\u6cd5\u662f\u4e00\u79cd\u57fa\u4e8e\u677e\u5f1b\uff08relax\uff09\u64cd\u4f5c\u7684\u6700\u77ed\u8def\u7b97\u6cd5\uff0c\u53ef\u4ee5\u6c42\u51fa\u6709\u8d1f\u6743\u7684\u56fe\u7684\u6700\u77ed\u8def\uff0c\u5e76\u53ef\u4ee5\u5bf9\u6700\u77ed\u8def\u4e0d\u5b58\u5728\u7684\u60c5\u51b5\u8fdb\u884c\u5224\u65ad\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1724913266, "style": "<style>.markdown-alert{padding:0.5rem 1rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:.25em solid var(--borderColor-default,var(--color-border-default));}.markdown-alert .markdown-alert-title {display:flex;font-weight:var(--base-text-weight-medium,500);align-items:center;line-height:1;}.markdown-alert>:first-child {margin-top:0;}.markdown-alert>:last-child {margin-bottom:0;}</style><style>.markdown-alert.markdown-alert-warning {border-left-color:var(--borderColor-attention-emphasis, var(--color-attention-emphasis));background-color:var(--color-attention-subtle);}.markdown-alert.markdown-alert-warning .markdown-alert-title {color: var(--fgColor-attention,var(--color-attention-fg));}</style>", "script": "<script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/GmeekTOC.js'></script><script>MathJax = {tex: {inlineMath: [[\"$\", \"$\"]]}};</script><script async src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mathjax@3/es5/tex-mml-chtml.js\"></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://github.githubassets.com/favicons/favicon.svg", "createdDate": "2024-08-29", "dateLabelColor": "#bc4c00"}, "P11": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/369ABC-ti-jie.html", "labels": ["Atcoder"], "postTitle": "369ABC\u9898\u89e3", "postUrl": "post/369ABC-ti-jie.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/Vynor/Vynor.github.io/issues/11", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 5223, "description": "# D - Bonus EXP # \r\n\u7b80\u5355DP\r\n\u8bbe\u7f6e $dp[i][j]$ \u4ee3\u8868\u8003\u8651\u9009\u62e9\u524d $i$ \u4e2a\u5143\u7d20\u51fb\u6740\uff0c\u51fb\u6740\u6b21\u6570\u7684\u5947\u5076\u6027\u662f $j(1 or 0)$\u7684\u6700\u5927\u503c\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1725178227, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/GmeekTOC.js'></script><script>MathJax = {tex: {inlineMath: [[\"$\", \"$\"]]}};</script><script async src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mathjax@3/es5/tex-mml-chtml.js\"></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://github.githubassets.com/favicons/favicon.svg", "createdDate": "2024-09-01", "dateLabelColor": "#bc4c00"}, "P13": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/yi-wei-de-yi-lai-ti-jie-shi-man-xing-si-wang.html", "labels": ["\u601d\u8003"], "postTitle": "\u4e00\u5473\u7684\u4f9d\u8d56\u9898\u89e3\u662f\u6162\u6027\u6b7b\u4ea1", "postUrl": "post/yi-wei-de-yi-lai-ti-jie-shi-man-xing-si-wang.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/Vynor/Vynor.github.io/issues/13", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 99, "description": "\u9898\u89e3\u662f\u68a6\u5e7b\